  <summary>An aesthetic, GPU-accelerated terminal emulator</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Flare is a modern terminal emulator forked from Alacritty and tailored for
      a more expressive desktop experience, while keeping Alacritty's fast and
      reliable terminal core.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Wayland native</li>
      <li>X11 native</li>
      <li>DE agnostic</li>
      <li>Runtime theme and opacity controls</li>
      <li>Custom tab and split-pane workflow</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

